quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,196,"“Indeed my Protector is Allah Who has sent down the Book; and He befriends the righteous.”"
  7,197,"“And those whom you worship besides Him cannot help you nor do they help themselves.”"
  7,198,"And if you call them to guidance they do not listen; and you (Prophet Mohammed – peace and blessings be upon him) observe them looking towards you, whereas they do not perceive anything."
  7,199,"And O dear Prophet (Mohammed – peace and blessings be upon him) adopt forgiveness, and enjoin virtue, and turn away from the ignorant."
  7,200,"And O listener! If the devil provokes you, seek the refuge of Allah; indeed He is All Hearing, All Knowing."
  7,201,"Indeed those who fear get alerted whenever a temptation from the devil troubles them, and they perceive immediately."
  7,202,"And the devils pull those who their brothers into error, and then do not make any relaxation."
  7,203,"And O dear Prophet (Mohammed – peace and blessings be upon him) when you do not bring to them a verse, they say, “Why did you not fabricate it?” Say, “I follow only what is divinely revealed to me from my Lord”; this (the Holy Qur’an) is an enlightenment from your Lord, and a guidance and a mercy for the Muslims."
  7,204,"And when the Qur’an is recited, listen to it attentively and keep silent, so that you receive mercy."
  7,205,"And remember your Lord within your hearts humbly and with fear, and softly with your tongues, morning and evening, and do not be of the neglectful."
  7,206,"Indeed those who are with your Lord are not conceited towards worshipping Him, and they proclaim His Purity and it is to Him they prostrate. (Command of Prostration # 1)"
